<page>
    <shortlink>howto create from template</shortlink>
    <topic>How do I Create a New Form Using a Template?</topic>
    <description>Forms in TranForm Cental can be created by coping built-in templates on the Design tab.</description>
    <sections>
        <section>
            <steps>
                <step>
                    <description>
                        <p>In *[extlink:TransForm Central@https://transform.alphasoftware.com]*, open the Designer tab.</p>
                    </description>
                </step>
                <step>
                    <description>
                        <p>Click the *[ui:+]* add button to add a new form. Then, click *[ui:Select Template]*.</p>
                    </description>
                    <figure>
                        <title>Create a new Form Design from Template</title>
                        <alt>Create a new Form Design from Template</alt>
                        <link>/images/selectTemplate.png</link>
                    </figure>
                </step>
                <step>
                    <description>
                        <p>A list of templates will be shown. Select the template you would like to use to create a new form.</p>
                    </description>
                    <figure>
                        <title>List of Form Templates</title>
                        <alt>List of Form Templates</alt>
                        <link>/images/formTemplates.png</link>
                    </figure>
                </step>
                <step>
                    <description>
                        <p>Finally, click *[ui:Click to save changes]* to save your new form design.</p>
                    </description>
                    <figure>
                        <title>Save Changes</title>
                        <alt>Save Changes</alt>
                        <link>/images/saveFormChanges.png</link>
                    </figure>
                </step>
            </steps>
        </section>
        <section>
            <description>
                <p>Your new form is ready to use. You can customize the form design using the *[ui:Edit Form Commands]* button in the Designer.</p>
            </description>
        </section>
    </sections>
</page>